            "title": "Maze Hunter",
            "shortDescription": "Maze-solving game in Java with JavaFX, fog-of-war, full statistics system, JSON persistence, and web deployment via TeaVM.",
            "fullDescription": "Maze Hunter is a feature-rich maze-solving game developed in Java using JavaFX and Maven. The game features procedurally generated mazes with multiple difficulty levels, fog-of-war mechanics, collectible items (crystals, energy cells, bombs), teleportation, and a complete statistics tracking system (Anales). Full game state persistence is achieved via GSON JSON serialization with save/load functionality. A per-screen background music system with volume control was implemented. The project was later compiled to WebAssembly via TeaVM for browser-based deployment on GitHub Pages.",
